UID:t1kxqKIJQiah4TNlhXCIr
SUMMARY:Dune Moss presented by The Triple Door at The Rabbit Box
DTSTAMP:20260410T044129Z
DTSTART:20260411T013000Z
DESCRIPTION:Dune Moss presented by The Triple Door at The Rabbit Box Friday
	\, April 10th / Doors 6:30pm / Music begins @ 7:30pm $20 General // $25 Ad
	vance Dune Moss is a woodland fairy who creates music that blends ethereal
	 magic\, indie electronic\, and art pop. Her music is inspired by artists 
	like Enya\, AURORA\, and Imogen Heap\, and aims to transport listeners to 
	another world. Moss grew up in a creative household and was inspired by he
	r mother's "majikal" playlist of movie soundtracks and other songs. She pl
	ays the accordion and sings and also designs and sells fairy wear on Etsy.
	 Buy Tickets\n\nhttps://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/dune-moss-
	presented-by-the-triple-door-at-the-rabbit-box/?occurrence=2026-04-10\n\nF
	rom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/dune-moss-presented-by-
	the-triple-door-at-the-rabbit-box/?occurrence=2026-04-10
LOCATION:The Rabbit Box\, 94 Pike Street Unit 11
